7. AI Safety And Security Considerations

The invention is designed as a non-clinical advisory maintenance framework.

The system:

* Does not modify therapy delivery
* Does not control patient treatment
* Does not suppress safety alarms
* Does not autonomously modify subsystem configuration
* Operates independently from patient-critical functions

The AI engine may operate locally within the embedded device environment without cloud connectivity.

The framework primarily analyzes:

* Hardware metrics
* Communication metrics
* Thermal metrics
* Operational subsystem behavior

No patient-identifiable information is required.

